ani饰）漂洋过海来到加拿大的Halifax寻找自己的爱人——英国军官Pinson（布鲁斯·罗宾逊 Bruce Robinson）。然而Pinson却已移情别恋，对Adele异常冷漠。Adele想尽一切方法想挽回Pinson皆告失败。而另一方面，当地高昂的生活费也让Adele难以承受，只能一次又一次要求父亲汇钱。此时的Hugo正流亡在一个小岛上，妻子病重，两人多次希望Adele能返回家中，但Adele坚持留在加拿大。恋情的失败让Adele经常想起她溺水身亡的姐姐，她的精神开始变得错乱。之后，Pinson跟着部队离开Halifax前往另一个小岛Barbados，Adele也跟随而去，在那里，她的病情日益恶化，最终被送回法国，在休养院里度过余生，最终于一战时期悄然离世。 本片是关于雨果二女儿Adele的传记片，扮演Adele的伊莎贝尔·阿佳妮获当年奥斯卡最佳女主角提名。", "description": "", "tags": [], "cover_url": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p1483320569.jpg", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2388255693.jpg", "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2213488281.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p692596622.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2315472362.jpg"], "actions": [], "sharing_url": "https://www.douban.com/doubanapp/dispatch/movie/1293870", "honor_infos": [{"kind": "movie", "uri": "douban://douban.com/subject_collection/ECYIOK3PY?type=rank&category=movie&rank_type=film_genre", "rank": 12, "title": "法国传记片榜"}], "good_rating_stats": 0, "subtype": "movie", "null_rating_reason": ""}}, {"item_type": "movie", "id": "26647163", "rank": 13, "name": "童年的许诺", "names": [], "links": ["https://movie.douban.com/subject/26647163/", "douban://douban.com/movie/26647163"], "covers": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2497696077.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2497696077.jpg"], "rating": {"count": 16158, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 8.2}, "score": 8.2, "vote": 16158, "summary": "2017 / 法国 比利时 / 爱情 传记 / 埃里克·巴比尔 / 皮埃尔·尼内 夏洛特·甘斯布", "ext": {"comment": "", "controversy_reason": "", "rank_value": 13, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2497696077.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2497696077.jpg"}, "is_show": false, "vendor_icons": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/f/frodo/88a62f5e0cf9981c910e60f4421c3e66aac2c9bc/pics/vendor